long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Secure Web World can hide your private WhatsApp sections like contacts, photos, and messages. You can use it in a meeting, public area, or office. Also, SWW can get back your deleted messages. You don't need to click anywhere in extension for those features, just download and go to web WhatsApp and you can go back to your work. SWW collect all your message in local storage and it never shares your messages to anyone. SWW is an open-source project, you can review codes and make your special changes.
